text: Bethel Census Area is a census area in the U.S. state of Alaska. As of the 2020 census, the population was 18,666. It is part of the Unorganized Borough and therefore has no borough seat. Its largest community is the city of Bethel, which is also the largest city in the Unorganized Borough. == References == Category:Alaska census areas
title: Bethel Census Area, Alaska
